    <body>
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center m-4">
            <p class="font-bold text-3xl text-[#009879]">About Us</p>
            <p class="bg-yellow-600 w-20 h-1"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex m-3">
            <div class="w-[50%] m-3 pt-3">
                <p class="text-lg">Welcome to CatFinder, your ultimate companion in finding the perfect feline friend! Whether
                    you’re a
                    seasoned cat lover or a first-time pet parent, we understand how important it is to choose the right
                    cat
                    for your home and lifestyle. Our mission is to connect you with the ideal cat for adoption, offering
                    a
                    wide variety of breeds, personalities, and needs to suit every type of cat lover.</p><br>

                <p class="text-lg">At CatFinder, we’ve created a user-friendly platform where you can browse through detailed profiles
                    of
                    different cat breeds, learn about their unique traits, and explore adoption options. We aim to make
                    the
                    adoption process smooth, informative, and fun!</p><br>

                <p class="text-lg">We believe that every cat deserves a loving home and that every person deserves a cat that matches
                    their
                    personality. Our website is designed to help you make an informed decision, whether you're looking
                    for a
                    playful kitten, a calm companion, or a specific breed with special care needs.</p><br>

                <p class="text-lg">Join us in making a difference—helping cats find their forever homes and making sure that you find a
                    furry friend who’s just right for you!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[50%] m-3">
                <img class="rounded h-[36rem] w-full p-3" src="styles/About-image.jpg" alt="Boy adopting a cat">
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>

